      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified-1\n\nTests uploaded by Trevis Autotest from trevis-3vm1 for review-dne-part-1 received by maloo, run on Red Hat Enterprise Linux Server 7.4/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/8528723e-cbdd-4c13-bb5f-b936fec34bee). Ran 7 tests. No failures.",
